info.description:
gasket-wsgi
======

A plug-in to the gasket architecture that provides WSGI support and XML display.

## Install updated `dict2xml`

You will need (in addition to pypi dependencies):

* dict2xml, but the github version, not the pypi version:
   
    pip install git+https://github.com/quandyfactory/dict2xml.git#egg=dict2xml

Contributors
============

* Jeremy G. Kahn <jeremy@trochee.net>
* pmariani for web-based display tools
info.name: gasket-wsgi
info.summary: WSGI view on gasket streams, including XML/javascript
